      <title>苏格兰民族党寻找领导人，苏格兰政府赢得信任投票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-01/scottish-government-wins-confidence-vote-as-snp-hunts-for-leader</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由即将离任的首席部长胡姆扎·优素福领导的苏格兰政府在反对党对其政府的不信任投票中幸存下来，执政的苏格兰民族党仍在寻找新的领导人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-01/scottish-government-wins-confidence-vote-as-snp-hunts-for-leader</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 14:40:17 GMT</pubDate>
