    <item>
      <title>土耳其希望加入南非联合国法庭对以色列提起的诉讼</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-01/turkey-wants-to-join-south-africa-s-un-court-case-against-israel</link>
      <description><![CDATA[土耳其正寻求加入南非在联合国最高法院提起的案件，作为原告指控以色列在巴勒斯坦加沙领土实施种族灭绝。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-01/turkey-wants-to-join-south-africa-s-un-court-case-against-israel</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 14:01:22 GMT</pubDate>
